FBIS4-33825 "drlat113_n_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-113 Daily Report 10 Jun 1994 Chile Carabineros Gen. Stange's Leave To Be Extended Carabineros Gen. Stange's Leave To Be Extended PY1106004794 Santiago Television Nacional de Chile Imagen Internacional in Spanish 1800 GMT 10 Jun 94 PY1106004794 Santiago Television Nacional de Chile Imagen Internacional Spanish BFN [Text] Defense Minister Edmundo Perez Yoma today asserted that the government deadline for Carabineros General Rodolfo Stange to modernize the Carabineros Institution will be extended. [Begin recording] [Unidentified reporter] Is it true that Gen. Stange will return to his post between 15 and 17 June? [Perez] Yes, based on the 30 days he asked for, he should return around the dates you have mentioned. I believe he will be unable to finish by then and there will probably have to be an extension. [Reporter] [question indistinct] [Perez] Because I believe he has not had enough time. [end recording]
